name: Flagship
Lore: 'After the Battle of Yavin, it was politically necessary to demonstrate the unstoppable might of the Empire. The Executor and Death Squadron ensured this objective.',
Text: 'Use 2 Force to deploy on your Star Destroyer. Your other starships may move as a ''react'' to same system or sector (for free). If starship lost, you lose X Force, where X = starship''s armor. (Immune to your Alter.)',
